description: This legacy package (libraries) is intended for projects imported from mikroC PRO for AVR into Necto studio, or suppose you want to quickly test your code in Necto Studio with libraries available in mikroC PRO for AVR. The package contains all libraries from mikroC PRO for AVR version v4.0.0, with improvements needed to work with Necto Studio.

boards.description: EasyAVR v7 is the seventh generation of our famous AVR development board. It is the product of accumulated knowledge over the past 10 years, and it is state of the art of design, functionality and quality. It is loved by beginners and hobbyists, as well as professionals, and used in education and development by thousands. Board comes with Atmega32 device.
This is a generic board definition. It can be combined with any of supported MCUs.
